Welcome to my portfolio project for Goldsmiths University.

To run this application on your local computer clone the repository from github.
Run npm install to install the dependencies for this application.
Ensure that MySQL in installed on your device and open it up in terminal.
Execute create_db.sql and then insert_data.sql to set up the database for the app.

Once that is complete you should be ready to run the application locally. Execute
node index.js to start the application and the app should be live on localhost:8000

Your app should be up and running now.